data.description: Extremely well maintained and decorated home in Germany Oaks Subdivision. 2670 square feet of living area that includes and elevated ceilings in the foyer, dining, living room and master bedroom area. This two story floor plan is equipped with smart home automation: QOLSYS IQ panel (central hub), skybell video doorbell, smart lightswitch, kwikset door lock, Honeywell programmable thermostat, WiFi garage door opener, Amazon Dot. Enjoy cooking and entertaining in the beautiful kitchen and breakfast nook that boost stainless steel appliances including Kitchen aid appliance package: Gas range, dishwasher, microwave. There is a large 3cm granite island, under mount sink and fantastic custom light fixtures, subway tile back splash and pull down kitchen faucet. The large downstairs main suite includes a private en suite bath that has a soaking tub and separate tiled shower, dual under mount rectangular vanities, over sized walk-in closet. Enjoy relaxing on the private patio off the main suite. This two story home has 1 1/2 baths downstairs as well as study and separate dining room. Upstairs you will find three more bedrooms, bathroom and spacious game/media room.  The home has a finished two car garage, fully sodded large lot with spacious patio. Outdoor kitchen with beer tap. Energy efficient radiant barrier in the attic as well as a 10-year warranty on the post tension slab. Upon entering our community you will be taken away with the majestic oak trees, lush green space, private lakes and shaded playground area for children.
